@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title Architektura systemu — backend

actor Klient
actor Kurier
actor "Pracownik punktu" as PointEmployee
actor Administrator

rectangle "Frontend SPA\n(React + TypeScript)" as Frontend
rectangle "REST API\n(Spring Boot)" as Api
rectangle "Warstwa biznesowa\nServices / Domain Logic" as Domain
rectangle "Persistence Layer\nRepositories / JPA" as Persistence

database "Oracle Database" as Oracle
cloud "System płatności\n(sandbox)" as PaymentGateway
cloud "OAuth2 Provider\n(np. Google)" as OAuth
queue "Message Queue\n(planowane)" as MQ

Klient --> Frontend
Kurier --> Frontend
PointEmployee --> Frontend
Administrator --> Frontend

Frontend --> Api : HTTP / JSON
Api --> Domain
Domain --> Persistence
Persistence --> Oracle

Api ..> OAuth : logowanie (później)
Domain ..> PaymentGateway : płatności (później)
Domain ..> MQ : powiadomienia / async (później)

note right of Domain
Główne moduły:
- Users & Roles
- Shipments
- Tracking
- Delivery Network
- Payments
- Complaints
- Reports
end note
@enduml
